name: The FEN roots
description: The FEN is a series of coordinated CryptoArt drops to encourage artists and collectors to transition their NFTs to a low-energy consumption blockchain. This project is initiated by independent curator Juliette Bibasse and visual artist Joanie Lemercier and made possible by pioneer digital artists and friends. Generative Type Design & Animation by Mike Brondbjerg (@mikebrondbjerg)
